data.enText: the type of whisky made in Scotland

data.chText: 你要不要喝一杯苏格兰威士忌？

value.def: Scotch or Scotch whisky is whisky made in Scotland.

posc.def: A Scotch is a glass of Scotch.

example.tran: 他为自己倒了一杯苏格兰威士忌。

value.def: Scotch means the same as Scottish. This use is considered incorrect by many people.
value.tran: 同 Scottish (许多人认为这种用法不正确)

trans: 苏格兰浓汤(用蔬菜和大麦煮成)
苏格兰香肠蛋(鸡蛋煮熟后外裹香肠肉和面包屑，炸后作为冷餐食用)
苏格兰霭(常见于苏格兰高地的有雨浓雾)
